features: Value Pack: This set includes 10 high-quality microfiber cloths, each measuring 6 x 7 inches (15cm x 18cm). It comes with 5 black and 5 white cloths, perfect for your daily cleaning needs or to share with family and friends.

Premium Quality Material: Made from soft, microfiber, these cleaning cloths are lint-free and gentle on delicate surfaces. Their tightly woven fibers attract fine dust, ensuring an effective and scratch-free clean. "

Perfect for Delicate Surfaces: These cloths are designed to safely clean dust, fingerprints, smudges, oils, and streaks from various surfaces like eyeglasses, mobile screens, jewelry, and other sensitive items without causing any damage.
Reusable & Long-Lasting: Economical, these microfiber cloths are easy to wash, quick to dry, and can be reused multiple times, making them a smart, budget-friendly cleaning solution.

Multipurpose Use: Ideal for cleaning eyeglasses, screens, cameras, jewelry, and more. These versatile cloths can be used on a wide range of surfaces, including mobile phones, tablets, car mirrors, and optical lenses.
